rong>品牌。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101736Y5RLymalZxHru0kO.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>8. 商业计划书</strong><span><strong>+</strong></span><strong>社交分享</strong><span><strong>+</strong></span><strong>天使轮。</strong><span><strong>@Joe</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144338IUKyFC6mxDdS0glO.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"355\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.59166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>9. 向 </strong><span><strong>XXX </strong></span><strong>提供 </strong><span><strong>XXX </strong></span><strong>的平台。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101737ELuwcn5AsUSzO3B6.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>10. 其实一直想……当一个作家。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101737vbs6whet9RrKXGAn.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.66727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>11. 其实一直想……当一个导演。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101738qOA0XphNak6cmiZ3.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.62146893\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>12. 其实一直想……</strong></span><strong>做音乐。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071017384bcJSkXP6zA1V5yM.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.54989817\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><strong>13. 其实一直想……红</strong></span><strong>。</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071017452KNZMIn5AwhdXiHF.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.596\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>14. 青年客栈。环球旅游。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101746tUD3pJB7XwyIWzCq.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.5225\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>15. 绿色。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101747mGZdc5johAigUpeq.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>16. 和朋友一起。TEAM。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071017487j9scFLZtv4QbUY0.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.642\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>17. </strong><strong>APP</strong><strong>。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101749euvVQ2p9h8baiCMS.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.67058824\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>18.  改变人们的……生活方式。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101750QUSkyvauMHjVb9cd.gif\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.75458716\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>19. 改变人们的……偏见。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101751vkcdTZoOpKeEWBVL.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>20. 改变人们的……的颜值。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101751dlaI3hz6kAmynuUN.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.79074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>21. 为个人和国家的经济做出贡献。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101752tWVTMRbZHNJLOlCu.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.73591549\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>22. 并不需要人类的感谢。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101752W8D6Zb5nAe0EMgf7.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.56612529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>23. 正好。说不定有艳遇。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607101753Lz3iuPUacYMHptRd.jpg\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" data-ratio=\"0.55183585\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>24. 所以。辞职。Yeah。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> <em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144338gKDQjmRFAb1YrfsC.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"303\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.606\" data-format=\"gif\"></em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>好奇心研究所的微博（</em></span><a href=\"http://weibo.com/p/1006065587974982/home?from=page_100606&amp;mod=TAB#place\" target=\"_blank\"><em>@好奇心研究所</em></a><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>）和微信公众号（ID：</em></span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>QLab42</em></span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em>）全面上线啦，微信直接搜索「好奇心研究所」就可以订阅，关注与所长亲密接触，赶紧的。</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\"><em></em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<em><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144339jpVJ4Xvd7bOrtYZQ.gif\" width=\"500\" height=\"226\" title=\"2\" alt=\"2\" dat